Name: athena-cviewd
Summary: Respond to cview requests for workstation status information
License: MIT
Group: Applications/Internet

Requires: athena-larv

%description
cviewd is normally run from inetd and contacted by the cview(1) or
xcluster(1) programs.  cviewd reads report files written by
larvnetd(8) and displays that information accord- ing to a one-line
command read from standard input (the net- work connection).  The
valid commands are described in cview(1).

